            <title>Keeta 外卖送错楼，网上客服竟建议事主去隔离楼找回</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/10/31/keeta-2/software/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=keeta-2</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/10/31/keeta-2/software/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Pickle Rick]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 07:00:47 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[应用软件]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[keeta]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[LIHKG]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Threads]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1272371</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>有网民在社交平台上分享用 Keeta 叫外卖的不快经历，指 Keeta 外卖员错送外卖到 60 米范围内的屋苑大厦，因而向客服投诉，但客服竟然要求事主自行找回外卖。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1272372 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/464987660_8554488084-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/464987660_8554488084-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/464987660_8554488084.jpg 415w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Keeta 外卖员错送外卖到 60 米范围内的屋苑大厦（图片来源：<a href="https://www.threads.net/@liannhoooo/post/DBwZvV7zniB">Threads</a>）</p><p>网民在 Threads 上发文抱怨，指自己于深夜用 Keeta 叫外卖，但 Keeta 外卖员错送外卖到 60 米范围内的屋苑大厦，叫事主自行找回外卖。事主怒斥：「送错地址叫我自己去揾，而家叫外卖定城市定向？」并表示香港环境密集，60 米内充斥不少楼宇，即使不计保安问题，都不能逐家逐户找外卖。最后，事主要求 Keeta 作书面回复，否则会向消委会投诉。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1272373 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/screenshot_20241031_-558x580.jpg" alt="" width="558" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/screenshot_20241031_-558x580.jpg 558w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/screenshot_20241031_.jpg 866w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 558px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲网民在 Threads 上发文怒斥 Keeta 客服，竟建议事主自行找回外卖（图片来源：<a href="https://www.threads.net/@liannhoooo/post/DBwZvV7zniB">Threads</a>）</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1272375 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/screenshot_20241031_-2-694x264.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="264" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/screenshot_20241031_-2-694x264.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/screenshot_20241031_-2.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲事主要求 Keeta 作书面回复，否则会向消委会投诉（图片来源：<a href="https://www.threads.net/@liannhoooo/post/DBwZvV7zniB">Threads</a>）</p><p>有网民留言称自己有相同经历，同样地，Keeta 客服也叫事主去自行寻回外卖。亦有连登网民指，Foodpanda 会直接退钱，不会叫事主自己找回外卖。有网民笑言：「祖国果然有另类的客服思想」。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1272374 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/screenshot_20241031_-1-694x163.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="163" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/screenshot_20241031_-1-694x163.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/screenshot_20241031_-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲有网民留言称自己有相同经历（图片来源：<a href="https://www.threads.net/@liannhoooo/post/DBwZvV7zniB">Threads</a>）</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1272376 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/screenshot_20241031_-694x207.png" alt="" width="694" height="207" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/screenshot_20241031_-694x207.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/screenshot_20241031_-1280x382.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/screenshot_20241031_.png 1408w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲连登网民指，Foodpanda 会直接退钱，不会叫事主自己找回外卖（图片来源：<a href="https://lihkg.com/thread/3812951/page/1">LIHKG</a>）</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1272377 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/screenshot_20241031_-1-1-694x345.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="345" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/screenshot_20241031_-1-1-694x345.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/screenshot_20241031_-1-1.jpg 876w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲有网民笑言：「祖国果然有另类的客服思想」（图片来源：<a href="https://www.threads.net/@liannhoooo/post/DBwZvV7zniB">Threads</a>）</p><p>资料及图片来源：<a href="https://www.threads.net/@liannhoooo/post/DBwZvV7zniB">Threads</a>、<a href="https://lihkg.com/thread/3812951/page/1">LIHKG</a>、<a href="https://kr-asia.com/meituans-keeta-launches-in-saudi-arabia-igniting-competition-and-price-hikes">KrASIA</a></p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
